OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will see sunny
OL,6,Fspells and scattered showers,
OL,7,Foccasionally heavy. This afternoon
OL,8,Fwill see bright spells with showers
OL,9,Fgradually dying out. Fewer showers
OL,10,Facross Angus.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRain will spread from the
OL,13,Fsouthwest during this evening and for
OL,14,Fa time in the early hours. Drier
OL,15,Fweather developing across most areas
OL,16,Flater in the night.
OL,17,
OL,18,CTuesday:FA dry and mostly cloudy day.
OL,19,FSome brightness breaking through
OL,20,Facross Fife and the Central Belt at
OL,21,Ftimes. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
