OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FCloudy, mild with rain on Wednesday,
OL,7,Fdrier with a few showers later.
OL,8,FBright, breezy with scattered showers
OL,9,Fon Thursday, mainly dry in the east.
OL,10,FRain for a time on Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
